OL,3,C"Our last chance at justice," says
OL,4,CPortsmouth woman given infected blood
OL,6,FA woman from Portsmouth who was given
OL,7,Finfected blood in the 1980s says the
OL,8,Foutcome of next week's Public Inquiry
OL,9,Fis, for many, a "last chance at
OL,10,Fjustice."
OL,12,FJackie Britton was infected with
OL,13,FHepatitis C from a transfusion
OL,14,Ffollowing the birth of her daughter in
OL,15,F1983. It has led to liver damage and
OL,16,Fworsening health.
OL,18,F"It's been traumatic in so many
OL,19,Fdifferent ways," she said.
