OL,3,C"Our last chance at justice," says
OL,4,CPortsmouth woman given infected blood
OL,6,F"Every time you go for your six month
OL,7,Fscans you think 'Will I be the next
OL,8,Fone with the death sentence?'
OL,10,F"For those that have campaigned for 30
OL,11,Fyears and existed instead of living
OL,12,Ftheir lives, it's disgusting.
OL,14,F"This inquiry was really important for
OL,15,Fmany of us. It's our last chance at
OL,16,Fjustice."
OL,18,FIn total, more than 3,000 patients are
OL,19,Fbelieved to have died.
