OL,6,FThe Infected Blood Inquiry has taken
OL,7,Ffive years to complete and cost #130
OL,8,Fmillion.
OL,10,FThe chairman, Sir Brian Langstaff is
OL,11,Fdue to release his final report next
OL,12,Fweek.
OL,14,FJackie was a key witness at the
OL,15,Finquiry and says at the she felt heard
OL,16,Fand listened to for the first time.
OL,18,FBut she says the battle for
OL,19,Faccountability and compensation from
OL,20,Fthe government stretching over decades
OL,21,Fhas made a terrible situation worse.
