OL,3,C"Our last chance at justice," says
OL,4,CPortsmouth woman given infected blood
OL,6,F"I don't think they could have handled
OL,7,Fa case of so many people so badly if
OL,8,Fthey'd tried."
OL,10,F"The trauma has been compounded by the
OL,11,Flength of time it has taken for us to
OL,12,Fbe listened to - by us having to tell
OL,13,Four stories over and over again - and
OL,14,Fwe do it because our dead have no
OL,15,Fvoices left, so we have to speak for
OL,16,Fthem."
