OL,3,C"Our last chance at justice," says
OL,4,CPortsmouth woman given infected blood
OL,6,F"For my own sanity l have to walk away
OL,7,Fat the end of this. I haven't got the
OL,8,Fstrength, the stamina or the time to
OL,9,Ffight any more."
OL,11,FA government spokesperson said: "This
OL,12,Fwas an appalling tragedy, and our
OL,13,Fthoughts remain with all those
OL,14,Fimpacted.
OL,16,F"We are clear that justice needs to be
OL,17,Fdelivered for the victims and have
OL,18,Falready accepted the moral case for
OL,19,Fcompensation.
