OL,3,C"Our last chance at justice," says
OL,4,CPortsmouth woman given infected blood
OL,6,F"This covers a set of extremely
OL,7,Fcomplex issues, and it is right we
OL,8,Ffully consider the needs of the
OL,9,Fcommunity and the far-reaching impact
OL,10,Fthat this scandal has had on their
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,F"The Government will provide an update
OL,14,Fto Parliament on next steps through an
OL,15,Foral statement within 25 sitting days
OL,16,Fof the Inquiry's final report being
OL,17,Fpublished."
